    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271752</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_110_020_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>マジで、こんなイナカに
英雄が住んでんのか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Are you telling me the great hero
&lt;Cless&gt; lives here, out in the sticks?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271872</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_110_020_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Klarth&gt;さんの
住んでた&lt;Red&gt;ユークリッド&lt;White&gt;も、
こういう感じだったでしょ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Well, &lt;Klarth&gt; lived in a village
quite similar to this one, right?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271980</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_110_020_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Klarth&gt;さんも確かに
時空戦士だけど、
&lt;Cless&gt;は違うんだぜ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Right, but even though &lt;Klarth&gt; might be an
Eternal Hero, &lt;Cless&gt; is completely different.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272048</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_110_020_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>違うって何が？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Different?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272380</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_110_020_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Cless&gt;は
時空戦士の
筆頭剣士なんだぞ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Cless&gt; is the Eternal Heroes' leading swordsman!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272380</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_110_020_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>エターナルソード持って、
先頭に立って魔王ダオスに
立ち向かったんだ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>He wielded the Eternal Sword, fought in
the war and faced off against Dhaos! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272380</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_110_020_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ダオス戦役の後は
&lt;Red&gt;トーティス&lt;White&gt;遊撃隊の隊長やって</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Before Dhaos's war began, he
was the head guard of &lt;Red&gt;Totus&lt;White&gt;.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272380</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_110_020_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Red&gt;ユークリッド&lt;White&gt;騎士団や
アルヴァニスタや、
世界中で活躍したんだぜ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>He was also part of &lt;Red&gt;Euclid's&lt;White&gt; and Alvanista's
Imperial Knights. Word of his accomplishments
spread throughout the world.</EnglishText>
      <Notes>Check please TL</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>3</BubbleId>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272456</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_110_020_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ふーん……
詳しいんだね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Mmm, how informative.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272916</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_110_020_014&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>まぁ、それはいいとして</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's great to hear, but...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>272916</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_110_020_015&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Cless&gt;さんを探すんでしょ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We should go search for &lt;Cless&gt;.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>273008</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_110_020_016&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>マクスウェルの手がかりも
見つけないと</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Let's also be on the lookout
for any clues about Maxwell.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
